### Authentication

#### [MODIFY] [frontend/src/context/AuthContext.jsx](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/context/AuthContext.jsx)
Replace the [login()](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/context/AuthContext.jsx#20-39) function from calling `api.post('/auth/login')` to simply comparing the entered password against `import.meta.env.VITE_APP_PASSWORD`.

