### Data Layer — Replace [api.js](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/lib/api.js) with Firestore

#### [MODIFY] [frontend/src/pages/ShopeeStock.jsx](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/ShopeeStock.jsx)
- [fetchStockData()](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/ShopeeStock.jsx#30-41): Replace `api.get('/data/prodStockCalc')` → `fetchCollection('shopeeProdStockCalc')`
- [handleSaveStock()](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/ShopeeStock.jsx#397-409): Replace `api.post('/data/prodStockCalc', stockData)` → batch-write each item back to Firestore using its document ID

#### [MODIFY] [frontend/src/pages/ProfitManager.jsx](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/ProfitManager.jsx)
- [fetchData()](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/ProfitManager.jsx#288-304): Replace `api.get('/data/prodActPriceCalc')` → Firestore. Source toggle (`shopee` / `tiktok`) maps to different collections:
  - Shopee: `shopeeProdActPriceCalc` and `shopeeOrgProductInfo`
  - TikTok: `tiktokProdActPriceCalcTikTok` and _(TikTok org info collection — not yet imported, will gracefully handle empty)_
- [persistSave()](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/ProfitManager.jsx#332-367): Replace `api.post` calls → batch Firestore writes

#### [MODIFY] [frontend/src/pages/IncomeCalculator.jsx](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/IncomeCalculator.jsx)
- [fetchProductInfo()](file:///E:/Software/CalculateShopeCostSummary/ShopeeWeb/frontend/src/pages/IncomeCalculator.jsx#23-40): Replace `api.get('/data/orgProductInfo')` → `fetchCollection('shopeeOrgProductInfo')`

